<Link id="l00279" /><CodeLine lineNumber="279"><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// prefix word and suffix word, i.e., prefixed&#95;instruction = concat(prefix&#95;word,</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
